 Mottola]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2008|| style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''''[[Tropic Thunder]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''[[Ben Stiller]]'''\n|-\n|''[[Burn After Reading]]'' || [[Coen brothers|Joel Coen and Ethan Coen]]\n|-\n|''[[Forgetting Sarah Marshall]]'' || [[Nicholas Stoller]]\n|-\n|''[[Role Models]]'' || [[David Wain]]\n|-\n|''[[Vicky Cristina Barcelona]]'' || [[Woody Allen]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2009|| style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''''[[The Hangover]]'''''\u00d7||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''[[Todd Phillips]]'''\n|-\n|''[[500 Days of Summer|(500) Days of Summer]]'' || [[Marc Webb]]\n|-\n|''[[It's Complicated (film)|It's Complicated]]'' || [[Nancy Meyers]]\n|-\n|''[[The Proposal (2009 film)|The Proposal]]'' || [[Anne Fletcher]]\n|-\n|''[[Zombieland]]'' || [[Ruben Fleischer]]\n|}\n\n===2010s===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=\"95%\" cellpadding=\"5\"\n|-\n!width=\"100\"|'''Year'''\n!width=\"450\"|'''Winner'''\n!width=\"450\"|'''Director(s)'''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2010|| style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''''[[Easy A]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''[[Will Gluck]]'''<ref>[http://www.mtv.com/news/2801954/critics-choice-movie-awards-winners/ 'The Social Network' Wins Big At Crtics' Choice Movie Awards - MTV]</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Cyrus (2010 comedy-drama film)|Cyrus]]'' || [[Jay Duplass]] and [[Mark Duplass]]\n|-\n|''[[Date Night]]'' || [[Shawn Levy]]\n|-\n|''[[Get Him to the Greek]]'' || [[Nicholas Stoller]]\n|-\n|''[[I Love You Phillip Morris]]'' || [[Glenn Ficarra]] and [[John Requa]]\n|-\n|''[[The Other Guys]]'' || [[Adam McKay]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2011|| style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''''[[Bridesmaids (2011 film)|Bridesmaids]]''''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''[[Paul Feig]]'''\n|-\n|''[[Crazy, Stupid, Love]]'' || [[Glenn Ficarra]] and [[John Requa]]\n|-\n|''[[Horrible Bosses]]'' || [[Seth Gordon]]\n|-\n|''[[